== Cruise ==
Cruises are the more expensive option. The location list is less than the vacation list. Unlike Vacations, parents do not decide to take their children or not in childhood. Cruises also bring [[Stats|happiness]] up higher than vacations. There are four cabin choices, listed from cheapest to priciest: Interior; Ocean View; Balcony; Suite.

